window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>From <i>USA Today</i> best seller Ava Harrison comes a sexy new stand-alone romance novel. </p> <p>Pierce Lancaster is bad news. Spoiled. Entitled. Sexy as - he's exactly what I don't want in my life. What I don't need. I'm not the girl he knew before. I've changed. </p> <p>But he hasn't. He's trouble filled with empty promises. I've come too far to fall back. </p> <p>Yet I can't seem to stay away. I can't say no. I am addicted to Pierce Lancaster.</p>"; 
